text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to have fun on a computer without using the internet?
text.Response A: You can play computer games, and watch movies and TV shows.  You can also use a computer to create music, or do some writing.
text.Response B: Sure, you can play lots of games on your computer. You can also use it to watch videos or listen to music.

Prompt

Can you tell me how to have fun on a computer without using the internet?

Response A

You can play computer games, and watch movies and TV shows. You can also use a computer to create music, or do some writing.

Response B

Sure, you can play lots of games on your computer. You can also use it to watch videos or listen to music.
